  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00925', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關社會保險的給付方面，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["其給付完全是現金給付", "於事故發生時，由社會保險之保險人直接給與被保險人或其家屬金錢", "通常給付與國民之薪資存在一定關係", "給付方式可一次性給付或持續性給付"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "df7cdcc487d5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "df191591992f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 49, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00926', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關中低收入戶老人請領生活津貼之規定，下列何者錯誤？', '["中低收入老人必須為未接受收容安置者，始得申請發給生活津貼", "雖已領有生活津貼，且其失能程度經評估為重度以上，而實際由家人照顧者，照顧者仍可向直轄市、 縣（市）主管機關申請發給特別照顧津貼", "不符合請領資格而領取津貼者，其領得之津貼，因為法律不溯及既往的原則，可以無須繳回", "津貼請領資格、條件、程序、金額及其他相關事項之辦法，由中央主管機關定之，並不得有設籍時間 之限制"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "df7cdcc487d5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "df191591992f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00927', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '政府僱用社會工作員開始於1970年代初期的臺灣省社會工作員實驗計畫，當時主要的工作業務是什麼？', '["個案工作和團體工作", "平價住宅和就業服務", "托兒育幼和老人安養", "社區發展和貧戶輔導"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00928', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作為一個助人專業，起源於英美，其歷史發展敘述，下列何者正確？', '["社會工作實行的方法及領域，全球都一致", "東歐國家社會工作的實施是以社會教育（socialpedagogue）為傳統", "第三世界國家，社會工作主要是透過國家發展來進行", "社會工作未來角色是以西方高度工業化的國家為基準"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00929', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '臺灣社會工作未來發展須回應社會變遷的需求，下列何者錯誤？', '["高科技對傳統社會工作干預技巧的挑戰", "案主需求不斷升高，但社會資源有限", "國家力量蓬勃，政府部門被信賴程度增加", "新的社會問題產生，如人口老化、失業、家庭暴力、貧窮等"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00930', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是保護性社會工作者的主要職責？', '["協助申請保護令", "陪同出庭", "轉介法律資源", "陪同案主接受宗教儀式去除惡運"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00931', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是災變社會工作者的主要職責？', '["評估案主受災狀況", "發放救濟物資與救濟金", "強制撤離時，請拒絕撤離的案主簽切結書", "勸導居民撤離危險地區"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00932', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '史基摩兒（Skidmore）等認為社會工作的功能有三種，下列何者不包括其中？', '["恢復受創的功能", "預防失調的功能", "資源提供與發展的功能", "促進變遷的功能"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00933', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據美國社會工作教育學會（CSWE）所訂立的教育政策與評鑑標準（EPAS），社會工作專業人才培育', '["價值與倫理", "研究", "媒體應用", "多元性  ⑤人類行為與社會環境  ⑥高 危險族群及社會與經濟的公平正義  ⑦社會福利政策與服務  ⑧法律  ⑨社會工作實務  ⑩實習"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00934', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作的價值，是一種專業的價值觀，它是專業的社會工作者在既有的社會價值中，選擇他們所推崇 的社會價值，形成屬於社會工作專業的價值體系。畢仁（Butrym,1976）在「社會工作的本質」（Thenature ofsocialwork）一書中，提出社會工作的基本價值有三項，下列何者不是此三項價值觀之一？', '["對人的尊重", "人有獨特的個性", "人有自我改變的能力", "人應致力於貢獻社會"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
